<text id="02-output-contract" title="Continuous Discovery Habits Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema draft-07 for the playbook-step artefact this methodology produces, with valid and invalid examples plus forbidden patterns.</summary>

  <section title="Schema (JSON Schema draft-07)">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/continuous-discovery-habits.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": [
    "tree_version",
    "outcome",
    "opportunities",
    "weekly_readout"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "tree_version": {
      "type": "string",
      "pattern": "^[0-9]{4}-Q[1-4]\\\\.[0-9]+$"
    },
    "outcome": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": [
        "id",
        "movability_check_passed"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "id": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "movability_check_passed": {
          "const": true
        }
      }
    },
    "opportunities": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 1,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "id",
          "shape",
          "quotes"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "shape": {
            "enum": [
              "problem",
              "unmet-need",
              "pain"
            ]
          },
          "quotes": {
            "type": "array",
            "minItems": 1,
            "items": {
              "type": "object",
              "required": [
                "participant_id",
                "interview_date",
                "verbatim"
              ],
              "properties": {
                "participant_id": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "interview_date": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "format": "date"
                },
                "verbatim": {
                  "type": "string",
                  "minLength": 10
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "weekly_readout": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": [
        "week",
        "interviews",
        "tree_diff"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "week": {
          "type": "string",
          "pattern": "^[0-9]{4}-W[0-9]{2}$"
        },
        "interviews": {
          "type": "integer",
          "minimum": 1
        },
        "tree_diff": {
          "type": "array"
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": true
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "tree_version": "2026-Q2.4",
  "outcome": {
    "id": "activation-rate-improved",
    "movability_check_passed": true
  },
  "opportunities": [
    {
      "id": "op-onboarding-friction",
      "shape": "pain",
      "quotes": [
        {
          "participant_id": "U_3471",
          "interview_date": "2026-05-19",
          "verbatim": "I had to scroll through six tabs before I figured out where to click create."
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "weekly_readout": {
    "week": "2026-W21",
    "interviews": 2,
    "tree_diff": [
      {
        "op": "add",
        "path": "/opportunities/0",
        "value": "op-onboarding-friction"
      }
    ]
  }
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "tree_version": "draft",
  "outcome": {
    "id": "growth",
    "movability_check_passed": false
  },
  "opportunities": [
    {
      "id": "build-onboarding",
      "shape": "problem",
      "quotes": []
    }
  ],
  "weekly_readout": {
    "week": "2026-21",
    "interviews": 0,
    "tree_diff": []
  }
}
]]></code>
    <note>tree_version pattern mismatch; outcome.movability_check_passed false; opportunity id is solution-shaped; quotes empty; week pattern mismatch; interviews must be &gt;= 1.</note>
  </example>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item>opportunity id phrased as 'build X' / 'add X' (solution-shaped).</item>
      <item>opportunity.quotes empty.</item>
      <item>weekly_readout.interviews &lt; 1 (skipped the weekly cadence).</item>
      <item>tree containing two outcomes (one-outcome-per-tree rule).</item>
      <item>quote without participant_id or interview_date.</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-continuous-discovery-habits.py">Validator script enforcing this schema</reference>
</text>
